headline: ADP to Present at Upcoming Investor Conference
summary: ADP (Nasdaq: ADP), a leading global technology company providing human capital management (HCM) solutions, today announced that it will present at the Nasdaq Investor Conference in London on Tuesday, December 10 at 3:00 a.m. ET / 8:00 a.m. GMT.
